{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/iOS-design-guide","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>A guide of standard practices, official guidelines(HIG) for designing iOS/iPadOS applications.</p>\n<p>This cheat sheet is mainly an attempt to keep track of wide variety of devices and their design constraints that are updated regularly.</p>\n<h4 id=\"display-specifications\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#display-specifications\" aria-label=\"display specifications permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Display Specifications</h4>\n<h6 id=\"iphone-models\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#iphone-models\" aria-label=\"iphone models permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>iPhone Models:</h6>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Device</th>\n<th align=\"center\">Size</th>\n<th align=\"center\">PPI</th>\n<th align=\"center\">Scale Factor</th>\n<th align=\"center\">Retina Display Name</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Portrait Resolution (points)</th>