2-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Icon Sizes</h6>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Icon Type</th>\n<th>Size (@1x)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Toolbar and Navigation Bar Icon</td>\n<td>22 x 22 px</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Tab Bar Icon</td>\n<td>25 x 25 px</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 id=\"typography\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#typography\" aria-label=\"typography permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Typography</h4>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Font Family</th>\n<th>Default system font</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Helvetica Neue</td>\n<td>iOS 8 and below</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>San Francisco</td>\n<td>iOS 9+</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Element</th>\n<th>Size (pt)</th>\n<th>Weight</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Navigation bar title</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>Semibold</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Large navigation bar title</td>\n<td>34</td>\n<td>Bold</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Buttons</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>Regular</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Search Bar</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>Regular</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Tab bar icon labels</td>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>Regular</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Table Row sublabel</td>\n<td>15</td>\n<td>Regular</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Table header</td>\n<td>13</td>\n<td>Regular</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Table Row</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>Regular</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Table Footer</td>\n<td>13</td>\n<td>Regular</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Action Sheets</td>\n<td>20</td>\n<td>Regular/ Semibold</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 id=\"referrences\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#referrences\" aria-label=\"referrences permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Referrences</h4>\n<p>I’ve managed to put this together for personal use as per my need using following useful links:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://kapeli.com/cheat_sheets/iOS_Design.docset/Contents/Resources/Documents/index\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Kapeli.com</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ivomynttinen.com/blog/ios-design-guidelines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ivomynttinen.com</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/design/resources/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Apple Design Resources</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/design/human-interface-guidelines/ios/overview/themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Human Interface Guidelines</a></li>\n</ul>","timeToRead":9,"frontmatter":{"title":"iOS design guide","date":"January 13, 2020","excerpt":"A guide of standard practices, official guidelines(HIG) for designing iOS/iPadOS applications. This cheat sheet is mainly an attempt to keep track of wide variety of devices and their design constraints that are updated regularly.","tag":"Design Guidelines","path":"/iOS-design-guide"}}},"pageContext":{"pagePath":"/iOS-design-guide","previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How 